{"tid":249881,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"是日高汁笑話","createTime":"2017-05-19T15:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T16:04:11.000Z","uid":69133,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4969d981010a202c760c13fc6a10b7c53c1ecb77","tid":249881,"uid":69133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T15:50:19.000Z","msg":"是咁的，本大師今日行街既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁行行下我聽到有條友叫我停低。<br />\n<br />\n咁我問佢乜撚野事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咁佢話佢電話唔見左想借我部電話黎打個電話。<br />\n<br />\n咁我就講........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嗰邊咪有電話亭囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁佢就過左去電話亭入邊之後暈低左，因為我岩先係入邊放撚左個臭屁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3abeb6368fd9bd522e4703626099daec705379","tid":249881,"uid":19778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T15:51:11.000Z","msg":"係咪爛gag黎？"},{"pid":"55515223c57ba758034c0ffe05b56ce0a32b562f","tid":249881,"uid":20622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T15:53:19.000Z","msg":"幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f307eb15889ede8804afac5fca63e14f75ff4e","tid":249881,"uid":15872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T15:54:04.000Z","msg":"高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8d5838f0f6bee2eb4c7c8eab13da202ad8ebf1","tid":249881,"uid":3500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T15:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac